        {
            "id": 6124627,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指上漲242.95點至12409.0059點，漲幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間25日10:51，深證成指上漲242.95點（或2%），暫報12409.01點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+4.57%</li><li>近 1 月：+8.69%</li><li>近 3 月：+20.07%</li><li>近 6 月：+10.77%</li><li>今年以來：+16.82%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>稀土永磁概念領漲+5.10%。其中    金力永磁(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300748:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300748\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300748-CN</a>)            上漲        20%            ;        正海磁材(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300224:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300224\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300224-CN</a>)            上漲        13.44%            ;        惠城環保(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300779:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300779\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300779-CN</a>)            上漲        10.5%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金屬鋅概念領漲+4.55%。其中    湖南<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002716:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002716\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002716-CN</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        盛達資源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000603-CN</a>)            上漲        6.92%            ;        中色股份(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000758:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000758\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000758-CN</a>)            上漲        5.1%    。</p></section></main>",
